											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="(Cine) En masse, the sisters fall on the Surgeon like the senators on Caesar. They stab and keep stabbing the Surgeon with their scalpels until there’s nothing left but a bloody mess. After it’s over, the sisters stay in place to perform a Sharran prayer. They’ve no regard for us - we’ve dealt with the Surgeon without having to combat him.&#xD;&#xA;" />
