											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="(Cine) The surgeon brings two of his scalpel fingers to his own eyes, then thrusts them in hard, all the way through and out of the back of his head. For a few moments he stands there in silence, the blood oozing richly out of his destroyed eyes and out of the exit wounds, then he collapses. It is over." />
